title: THE MOST EXCITED I'VE BEEN SINCE MY LIPSTICKS!
author: Jaclyn Hill
description:
I'm so excited to announce my new Bougie Rouge collection!!! This collection is inspired by the rosy romance of the 18th century royalty! I've been working on this product for two years and am so excited to see the looks you create with it! 🍾

Launching 6/10/21 @ 11am PST exclusively on jaclyncosmetics.com

💘 Mood Light Luminous Rouge - $30
Experience a subtle, luminous veil of color with this radiant loose powder blush.
(Available in 4 shades)

💘 Rouge Romance Cream-to-Powder Blush Stick - $22
This cream-to-powder blush stick transforms on skin for a gorgeous, effortless wash of color.
(Available in 4 shades)

💘 Rouge Romance Matte Blush Palettes - $45
These dreamy palettes features 6 beautiful, long-wearing shades in a silky-soft, matte finish.
(Available in 2 palettes - Cool & Warm toned)

💘 Rouge Romance Lip Cushion - $18
Get rich, creamy lip color in blushing hues with an ultra-lightweight, blurring finish.
(Available in 5 shades)
